                        <interp inst="t18450616-name-1084" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>MR. JOHN FIELD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am inspector of coin to the Royal Mint—these are both counterfeit.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> As to what Mr. Coles states it is correct; but at to Mrs. Weller it is entirely false; I was ten miles away at the time.</p>
